The paper deals with the problem of effective SLAM using a single monocular camera, which is a topic in robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the use of reinforcement learning (RL) to generate fail-safe trajectories, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves computer vision techniques for SLAM (cs.CV) and system control for trajectory planning (cs.SY).
